Package synchronizer

Class FileDistributedSynchronization

  • java.lang.Object
    • synchronizer.Synchronization
      • synchronizer.DistributedSynchronization
        • synchronizer.FileDistributedSynchronization
  • public class FileDistributedSynchronization
extends DistributedSynchronization
    A class responsible for the creation of instances of all classes of this package needed at startup time when distributed synchronization is used. The creation method used by this class requires a textfile from which the number of PersonalSynchronizer instances are read.
